				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\Omega$$\end{document} m ), the values have to be trusted. Furthermore, information (depth and/or resistivity) is missing in some points, which are excluded from the study. It results in 1521 interpreted points in the second part of the data.

